WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
MARYLAND TO BAHAMAS.
DNC 15, DNC 16, DNC 17.
1. 34 FOOT S/V ANEMONE, CREAM HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
   OVERDUE MARYLAND (39-16-37N 076-10-02W)
   TO BAHAMAS (25-04-00N 077-20-00W) ON 15 JAN.
   LAST KNOWN POSITION (38-59-30N 076-22-20W) ON 17 JAN.
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
   ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC BOSTON,
   PHONE: 617 223 8555, E-MAIL: RCCBOSTON@USCG.MIL.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 831/15.
